27
00:01:31.900 --> 00:01:33.530
Army of One

28
00:01:33.530 --> 00:01:37.330
I can't believe they managed
to restrain you, Master Sasaki.

29
00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:39.500
Pretty dumb, right?

30
00:01:39.870 --> 00:01:43.920
I never thought Kyoshiro, my so-called
friend, would trick me like this.

31
00:01:47.960 --> 00:01:49.090
Now...

32
00:01:49.090 --> 00:01:50.920
What the hell caused this?

33
00:01:50.920 --> 00:01:55.180
Well, Big Mom was fighting in the dome...

34
00:01:55.180 --> 00:01:57.560
And her attack made it all the way out here?!

35
00:01:58.310 --> 00:02:00.680
That's some insane strength.

36
00:02:00.680 --> 00:02:03.270
Well, at least it got me free.

37
00:02:03.940 --> 00:02:08.360
Anyway, I can't believe Kyoshiro
was one of Oden's retainers.

38
00:02:10.650 --> 00:02:14.820
I don't give a rat's ass about Wano's history...

39
00:02:15.410 --> 00:02:18.280
but he's going to regret double-crossing me!

40
00:02:24.870 --> 00:02:26.330
Charge!

41
00:02:34.090 --> 00:02:36.760
We shall put an end to this!

42
00:02:47.560 --> 00:02:50.690
Exterminate the minks!

43
00:02:51.150 --> 00:02:52.940
You cannot break our will!

44
00:02:52.940 --> 00:02:55.150
We will take you-gara down!

45
00:02:55.150 --> 00:02:57.870
Go ahead and do your worst.

46
00:03:05.370 --> 00:03:07.330
This will finish you off!

47
00:03:25.600 --> 00:03:27.400
Let us take care of the rest!

48
00:03:27.770 --> 00:03:28.980
Wait.

49
00:03:30.150 --> 00:03:31.480
Kin'emon.

50
00:03:33.860 --> 00:03:35.700
Dog! Cat!

51
00:03:36.490 --> 00:03:38.950
Let us handle this.

52
00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:40.280
Indeed.

53
00:04:22.030 --> 00:04:22.830
Such speed!

54
00:04:43.550 --> 00:04:46.020
It's not just the Straw Hats...

55
00:04:46.640 --> 00:04:50.020
Those are totally Udon prisoners.

56
00:04:51.060 --> 00:04:53.270
Even Hyogoro's down there!

57
00:04:53.270 --> 00:04:57.650
What happened at the prisoner
mining camp in Udon?

58
00:04:58.440 --> 00:05:01.110
Did they threaten Babanuki?

59
00:05:01.240 --> 00:05:05.410
This is Warden Babanuki in Udon.

60
00:05:05.410 --> 00:05:12.040
Straw Hat Luffy, Captain Kid, and all
the troublemakers are locked in their cells.

61
00:05:12.040 --> 00:05:14.840
So, I called to tell you all is well.

62
00:05:16.340 --> 00:05:18.170
This doesn't add up.

63
00:05:22.180 --> 00:05:24.640
I'm not going to blame you for all this.

64
00:05:24.640 --> 00:05:27.770
After all, you've always been brainless.

65
00:05:27.770 --> 00:05:30.890
You didn't have to say all that other crap!

66
00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:35.690
We need to take care of this
situation immediately.

67
00:05:35.690 --> 00:05:38.360
Now you sound like a leader!

68
00:05:40.030 --> 00:05:42.150
Damn that Straw Hat!

69
00:05:44.740 --> 00:05:48.290
Onigashima is in chaos...

70
00:05:48.290 --> 00:05:49.160
Hawkins.

71
00:05:49.750 --> 00:05:53.210
It wasn't your choice to join the Beast Pirates.

72
00:05:54.040 --> 00:05:56.170
If you're planning to defect, now's the time...

73
00:05:56.170 --> 00:05:58.840
Are you really asking me to betray them?

74
00:05:59.840 --> 00:06:00.800
I'm no fool.

75
00:06:03.050 --> 00:06:04.890
One percent.

76
00:06:05.300 --> 00:06:07.260
What are you trying to predict?

77
00:06:08.260 --> 00:06:11.730
The probability that a certain someone
survives until tomorrow.

78
00:06:12.100 --> 00:06:13.770
Only one percent, huh...?

79
00:06:14.350 --> 00:06:15.350
Poor bastard.

80
00:06:20.190 --> 00:06:22.820
Come in, Soaring Six.

81
00:06:24.530 --> 00:06:26.200
How annoying!

82
00:06:26.200 --> 00:06:27.870
What do you want, King?!

83
00:06:28.330 --> 00:06:29.240
Everyone...

84
00:06:29.830 --> 00:06:31.160
As you know...

85
00:06:31.830 --> 00:06:33.790
the situation has changed.

86
00:06:34.500 --> 00:06:37.000
On the day of the annual Fire Festival,

87
00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:41.460
we let the Red Scabbards samurai,
of all enemies, invade.

88
00:06:42.590 --> 00:06:46.680
This is the biggest blunder
in Onigashima's history.

89
00:06:48.720 --> 00:06:53.520
We must set aside our internal struggle,
even if Kaido encouraged it.

90
00:06:53.850 --> 00:06:55.100
Our what?

91
00:06:55.100 --> 00:06:57.270
This is regarding Young Master Yamato.

92
00:06:57.610 --> 00:07:00.730
The one who returns
Young Master Yamato home...

93
00:07:01.150 --> 00:07:05.660
earns the right to challenge
any of the Superstars for their position.

94
00:07:06.860 --> 00:07:08.870
Although it pains me to say this,

95
00:07:09.280 --> 00:07:11.990
we must put this on hold for the time being.

96
00:07:11.990 --> 00:07:13.620
What?! Seriously?!

97
00:07:13.620 --> 00:07:14.790
Of course.

98
00:07:15.410 --> 00:07:18.290
Look around you, Big Sis.

99
00:07:18.290 --> 00:07:21.090
Oh, Pay-Pay! Just who I was looking for!

100
00:07:21.590 --> 00:07:26.130
Yamato got away by climbing the wall,
so you have to give me a piggyback ride...

101
00:07:26.130 --> 00:07:26.800
No way.

102
00:07:26.800 --> 00:07:27.720
You have to!

103
00:07:27.720 --> 00:07:29.430
Shut up, you stupid kids.

104
00:07:30.470 --> 00:07:31.970
– Who are you calling a kid?!
– Who are you calling a kid?!

105
00:07:31.970 --> 00:07:34.850
I'm not a kid anymore! Don't call me that!

106
00:07:34.230 --> 00:07:36.230
Kaido is up on the rooftop.

107
00:07:37.190 --> 00:07:40.900
The enemy is going to climb
to the top of the castle from the inside.

108
00:07:41.610 --> 00:07:45.280
All of you will need to do
whatever you can to stop them.

109
00:07:45.900 --> 00:07:48.410
Our troops number 30,000.

110
00:07:48.410 --> 00:07:51.910
Their troops only number 5,000.

111
00:07:52.330 --> 00:07:55.710
Still, don't underestimate them.

112
00:07:55.710 --> 00:07:57.580
Good luck.

113
00:08:03.090 --> 00:08:04.670
Hey, Drake!

114
00:08:04.670 --> 00:08:07.090
There's an opportunity in all this mess.

115
00:08:07.090 --> 00:08:08.720
Take a walk with me.

116
00:08:08.720 --> 00:08:10.850
I can't handle it on my own.

117
00:08:11.890 --> 00:08:13.220
Where are you going?

118
00:08:13.220 --> 00:08:15.680
To kill the man I want to kill!

119
00:08:16.560 --> 00:08:18.600
Let's pay Queen a visit.

120
00:08:18.600 --> 00:08:21.690
Don't get me involved in your little spat.

121
00:08:21.690 --> 00:08:23.650
Do you wanna weaken our forces?

122
00:08:23.650 --> 00:08:25.610
He's useless anyway.

123
00:08:26.150 --> 00:08:28.200
I'm not sure about this...

124
00:08:30.610 --> 00:08:32.580
Straw Hats!

125
00:08:32.580 --> 00:08:35.950
Allow us to clear the way to the castle!

126
00:08:35.950 --> 00:08:41.170
Indeed! Conserve your strength
for the battle ahead!

127
00:08:47.090 --> 00:08:49.260
Charge!

128
00:08:49.260 --> 00:08:54.140
Get Straw Hat and his allies into the castle!

129
00:09:08.490 --> 00:09:10.030
Don't allow them to recover!

130
00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:12.160
They're just prisoners and yakuza!

131
00:09:16.240 --> 00:09:18.080
How amazingly chaotic.

132
00:09:23.880 --> 00:09:26.460
We must eliminate the large one, as well!

133
00:09:26.460 --> 00:09:28.960
I can't believe such a human exists.

134
00:09:29.340 --> 00:09:31.720
Do not hesitate! We must take him down!

135
00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:33.470
Attack his feet!

136
00:10:06.670 --> 00:10:09.130
Oh my, that was close.

137
00:10:10.670 --> 00:10:11.800
Jinbe!

138
00:10:43.960 --> 00:10:47.170
That's enough, you two.

139
00:10:52.510 --> 00:10:53.550
Kaido!

140
00:10:54.760 --> 00:10:59.260
Jack is one of my handpicked Superstars!

141
00:10:59.260 --> 00:11:05.480
I won't just sit idly by as you
beat one of my best men to death.

142
00:11:05.480 --> 00:11:08.860
Please... forgive me...

143
00:11:08.860 --> 00:11:10.400
Viceroy Kaido...

144
00:11:10.860 --> 00:11:14.530
You're no weakling, Jack.

145
00:11:15.320 --> 00:11:17.360
It's just that these guys...

146
00:11:20.160 --> 00:11:22.410
are too strong!

147
00:11:27.460 --> 00:11:32.460
Thanks to these Sulongs,
we've taken serious losses...

148
00:11:33.010 --> 00:11:38.050
But you did a good job
fending them off as well as you did.

149
00:11:38.550 --> 00:11:40.430
Go get yourself patched up.

150
00:11:40.430 --> 00:11:42.510
You've already done plenty.

151
00:11:44.480 --> 00:11:46.980
What the hell is going on?!

152
00:11:46.980 --> 00:11:50.270
You should be asking yourself that question!

153
00:11:53.400 --> 00:11:58.530
You let Trafalgar Law escape
in the Flower Capital, didn't you?

154
00:11:58.530 --> 00:12:00.530
We had a guard posted...

155
00:12:00.530 --> 00:12:04.290
I figured it must have been you.

156
00:12:04.290 --> 00:12:06.250
What's your objective?

157
00:12:06.250 --> 00:12:08.040
I see...

158
00:12:08.040 --> 00:12:09.880
The one you wanted to kill is...

159
00:12:09.880 --> 00:12:12.000
...you, you piece of shit!

160
00:12:12.540 --> 00:12:15.840
We should be ashamed
that we had a rat among our ranks.

161
00:12:15.840 --> 00:12:17.800
What are you up to?

162
00:12:17.800 --> 00:12:21.430
Are you working alone, or with a group?

163
00:12:21.430 --> 00:12:23.470
Just who exactly are you?!

164
00:12:27.020 --> 00:12:28.600
I guess this is it...

165
00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:30.350
I can't talk myself out of this.

166
00:12:31.900 --> 00:12:33.570
Unfortunately...

167
00:12:34.190 --> 00:12:37.440
I won't talk even if you kill me!

168
00:12:37.440 --> 00:12:39.950
Oh, I'm not gonna kill you...

169
00:12:39.950 --> 00:12:43.580
My kind of torture
will break your spirit instead.

170
00:12:46.160 --> 00:12:51.130
Bet you can't wait, huh, Drake?

171
00:12:52.420 --> 00:12:53.920
Damn monster...

172
00:12:56.670 --> 00:12:58.130
Straw Hat!

173
00:12:58.130 --> 00:13:00.090
That thing is just like Oars.

174
00:13:00.090 --> 00:13:06.020
Back then, it took all of us together
to bring down something that huge!

175
00:13:08.100 --> 00:13:09.730
But things are different now!

176
00:13:16.570 --> 00:13:17.480
Luffy!

177
00:13:25.200 --> 00:13:27.160
Gear Fourth!

178
00:13:28.160 --> 00:13:30.330
Boundman!

179
00:13:32.880 --> 00:13:35.000
Oh, he did it again!

180
00:13:35.000 --> 00:13:38.300
That form... He looks
just like a guardian deity!

181
00:13:56.270 --> 00:13:57.270
All right.

182
00:13:57.270 --> 00:13:58.690
Huh?!

183
00:13:58.690 --> 00:14:00.940
What, not interested in the torture?

184
00:14:00.940 --> 00:14:02.820
What a bummer...

185
00:14:04.450 --> 00:14:05.280
Why don't I...

186
00:14:06.080 --> 00:14:08.330
leave you all...

187
00:14:09.040 --> 00:14:10.330
a parting gift?

188
00:14:12.920 --> 00:14:13.580
Take cover!

189
00:14:20.090 --> 00:14:22.340
Now what? How do I get away?

190
00:14:22.930 --> 00:14:24.970
Is there no way back to the Marines?!

191
00:14:25.590 --> 00:14:26.300
No!

192
00:14:26.300 --> 00:14:28.310
No time to think about that now!

193
00:14:32.680 --> 00:14:35.850
There's still one hope left!

194
00:14:38.940 --> 00:14:41.360
Gum-Gum...

195
00:14:42.440 --> 00:14:43.700
Get out of my way...

196
00:14:43.700 --> 00:14:45.240
Juki!

197
00:14:47.530 --> 00:14:49.490
X...

198
00:14:51.410 --> 00:14:52.620
...Kong...

199
00:14:52.620 --> 00:14:54.040
...Gun!
...Calibur!

200
00:15:28.120 --> 00:15:28.820
That's...

201
00:15:28.820 --> 00:15:30.870
...Drake of the Soaring Six!

202
00:15:30.870 --> 00:15:32.950
Why did he attack the giant?!

203
00:15:37.370 --> 00:15:38.960
There's still...

204
00:15:40.630 --> 00:15:41.500
hope.

205
00:15:49.220 --> 00:15:50.140
Crap!

206
00:15:50.140 --> 00:15:53.350
Luffy is amazing!

207
00:15:53.350 --> 00:15:55.060
Straw Hat Luffy!

208
00:15:55.680 --> 00:15:58.350
I can't say why, but I've
just become an army of one!

209
00:16:00.480 --> 00:16:01.150
Please!

210
00:16:01.860 --> 00:16:05.070
Allow me to fight on your side!

211
00:16:06.860 --> 00:16:08.320
Huh?!

212
00:16:22.210 --> 00:16:24.670
What's with that guy?

213
00:16:24.670 --> 00:16:26.880
He wants to fight with us?!

214
00:16:27.220 --> 00:16:33.810
He's that perv who saw Nami and Robin taking
a bath the other day in the Flower Capital!

215
00:16:33.810 --> 00:16:37.770
He just turned into some kind of dinosaur!

216
00:16:37.770 --> 00:16:40.850
He must be one of those Soaring Six officers.

217
00:16:41.900 --> 00:16:44.940
But... something's strange...

218
00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:47.740
What in the world does he think he's doing?!

219
00:16:47.740 --> 00:16:49.360
Hey, Drake!

220
00:16:49.360 --> 00:16:51.570
Why did you attack one of the Numbers?!

221
00:16:52.120 --> 00:16:54.790
Luffy is amazing!

222
00:16:56.120 --> 00:16:58.080
He just makes you feel like...

223
00:16:58.080 --> 00:17:00.750
like you're super close if you're friends,

224
00:17:00.750 --> 00:17:04.250
but if you become his enemy,
he'll leave you in the dust.

225
00:17:04.250 --> 00:17:07.880
That's the kind of guy he is!

226
00:17:08.510 --> 00:17:10.050
What do you mean?

227
00:17:10.050 --> 00:17:13.890
Luffy has this aura that draws people to him!

228
00:17:18.730 --> 00:17:20.600
I know you!

229
00:17:20.600 --> 00:17:22.270
You wanna take down Kaido too?!

230
00:17:22.810 --> 00:17:26.480
I can't tell you why,
but we have the same goal!

231
00:17:33.950 --> 00:17:37.660
Don't try to pull anything on us right now!

232
00:17:37.660 --> 00:17:38.290
Luffy!

233
00:17:39.290 --> 00:17:43.750
He's working for Kaido now,
just like Hawkins!

234
00:17:45.170 --> 00:17:48.130
I was just removed from my position!

235
00:17:49.550 --> 00:17:51.970
That's why you wanna side with us?!

236
00:17:51.970 --> 00:17:55.350
How can we trust that two-timer?!

237
00:17:55.350 --> 00:17:58.970
Stay away from Luffy, X Drake!

238
00:17:59.600 --> 00:18:03.520
Even the world of pirates
is governed by a code of honor!

239
00:18:27.290 --> 00:18:29.250
Sure, we can team up.

240
00:18:29.250 --> 00:18:30.420
– No way!
– No way!

241
00:18:30.420 --> 00:18:33.430
Stay out of this, Captain!
You're such a dumbass!

242
00:18:38.680 --> 00:18:41.560
Hurry to the castle, Luffy!

243
00:18:41.560 --> 00:18:42.980
Okay!

244
00:18:42.980 --> 00:18:44.230
I'll leave them to you!

245
00:18:47.020 --> 00:18:49.860
Sanji! Let's get inside the castle!

246
00:18:49.860 --> 00:18:51.030
Yeah!

247
00:18:51.030 --> 00:18:52.940
The man in the straw hat...

248
00:18:52.940 --> 00:18:56.370
I guess he's the boss
of all these pirates and samurai!

249
00:18:56.700 --> 00:18:58.410
Let's go, Big Sis!

250
00:18:58.830 --> 00:19:01.790
Keep those two away from Straw Hat!

251
00:19:01.790 --> 00:19:03.160
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

252
00:19:03.160 --> 00:19:05.540
Move it, samurai!

253
00:19:05.540 --> 00:19:08.840
You ultra-incompetent bumbling buffoons!

254
00:19:24.640 --> 00:19:27.810
I fought those two in the castle!

255
00:19:27.810 --> 00:19:28.900
That's...

256
00:19:34.440 --> 00:19:36.950
the dinosaur from the Flower Capital!

257
00:19:37.820 --> 00:19:38.820
But...

258
00:19:40.080 --> 00:19:42.910
who's that cutie right beside him?!

259
00:19:45.120 --> 00:19:49.210
You'll never see Kaido again!

260
00:19:49.210 --> 00:19:50.880
Straw Hat!

261
00:19:50.880 --> 00:19:53.630
Lethal... Green Star!

262
00:19:58.720 --> 00:20:01.260
Skull Bombgrass!

263
00:20:08.600 --> 00:20:09.900
Pay-Pay!

264
00:20:15.190 --> 00:20:17.070
Wh-Who is that?!

265
00:20:20.780 --> 00:20:22.490
I'm Nami!

266
00:20:22.490 --> 00:20:24.410
What's your problem?!

267
00:20:24.870 --> 00:20:27.410
Nothing I like more than exterminating lizards.

268
00:20:27.410 --> 00:20:29.790
Now prepare yourself!

269
00:20:30.670 --> 00:20:32.590
What the hell are you doing?!

270
00:20:33.420 --> 00:20:35.260
Lizards?!

271
00:20:37.340 --> 00:20:41.090
Prepare to be sprayed with lizard killer!

272
00:20:41.090 --> 00:20:42.180
Don't hide!

273
00:20:43.850 --> 00:20:46.270
How dare you shoot me!

274
00:20:46.270 --> 00:20:49.310
Just who the hell did that?!

275
00:20:49.640 --> 00:20:51.270
Oh, Pay-Pay!

276
00:20:51.270 --> 00:20:53.150
It was that detestable tramp!

277
00:20:53.690 --> 00:20:54.730
That's right!

278
00:20:54.730 --> 00:20:58.490
I am the Great Lizard Buster, Nami!

279
00:20:58.490 --> 00:20:59.860
Remember my name!

280
00:20:59.860 --> 00:21:01.490
Knock it off already!

281
00:21:03.530 --> 00:21:06.240
It wasn't me, but whatever!

282
00:21:06.240 --> 00:21:08.620
The battle is already on!

283
00:21:09.920 --> 00:21:10.830
Now...

284
00:21:12.380 --> 00:21:14.460
Bring it on!

285
00:21:15.250 --> 00:21:15.300
What?!

286
00:21:15.300 --> 00:21:15.340
What?!

287
00:21:15.340 --> 00:21:15.380
What?!

288
00:21:15.380 --> 00:21:17.420
What?!

289
00:21:19.840 --> 00:21:22.180
Your words don't match your actions!

290
00:21:22.180 --> 00:21:23.890
Look who's talking!

291
00:21:23.890 --> 00:21:26.180
I won't let you get away!

292
00:21:26.180 --> 00:21:28.230
How could you hurt Pay-Pay?!

293
00:21:28.230 --> 00:21:29.270
Look...

294
00:21:29.270 --> 00:21:30.270
...how fast...

295
00:21:30.270 --> 00:21:33.150
– ...we can run away!
– ...we can run away!

296
00:21:33.150 --> 00:21:35.520
– Hold it!
– Hold it!

297
00:21:37.110 --> 00:21:40.320
– Stop!
– Stop!

298
00:21:40.780 --> 00:21:42.530
I'm counting on you, Usopp!

299
00:21:42.530 --> 00:21:44.160
Protect my Nami!

300
00:21:44.570 --> 00:21:47.450
Come on, Luffy! Let's meet up
with Kin'emon's group!

301
00:21:47.450 --> 00:21:48.540
Yeah!

302
00:21:55.460 --> 00:21:56.670
Hey, Sanji!

303
00:21:56.670 --> 00:21:57.960
Cover your ears!

304
00:21:58.960 --> 00:22:00.340
